  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Calculatable
    An interface of the methods that are used in calculations.
    Displayable
    An interface of the Display method.
    freqPassenger
    An interface that has the functionality allowed to frequent passengers only and extends the common functionalities of all passengers to apply Interface segregation principle.
    guest
    An interface that has the functionality allowed to guest passengers only and extends the common functionalities of all passengers to apply Interface segregation principle.
    Passengers
    An interface of the Functionalities that the passengers can do.
